.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Claude Code auto-memory should NEVER live in the project tree.
# The canonical path is ~/.claude/projects/<encoded-project>/memory/.
# If a stray `memory/` ever appears here it's an artifact from an earlier
# session writing to the wrong path — ignore it so it can't pollute
# `git status` or be committed by accident.
/memory/
